data.description: Quaint 3 bed, 2 bath house located in the highly sought after Benton County. Less than 30 min from downtown Bentonville! Property includes approximately 2.5 acres of beautiful hardwoods, as wells as, an enclosed sun porch, and a large fenced in back yard. The house has had some updates done to it and is completely livable but could still be continually updated as the buyer sees fit. Don't miss out on this opportunity! Schedule your showing today!
